methods.findKeys:
Find keys and deliver them to the locationKeyObserver.

:param locationKeyObserver: (java.util.function.Consumer<DeephavenNestedPartitionLayout.TLK>) - Per-key callback
methods.forParquet:
:param tableRootDirectory: java.io.File
:param tableName: java.lang.String
:param columnPartitionKey: java.lang.String
:param internalPartitionValueFilter: java.util.function.Predicate<java.lang.String>
:return: io.deephaven.parquet.table.layout.DeephavenNestedPartitionLayout<io.deephaven.parquet.table.location.ParquetTableLocationKey>

text:
TableLocationKeyFinder that will traverse a directory hierarchy laid out in Deephaven's "nested-partitioned"
 format, e.g.
 
 
 tableRootDirectory/internalPartitionValue/columnPartitionValue/tableName/...
 
 
 , producing FileTableLocationKey's with two partitions, for keys "__INTERNAL_PARTITION__" and the
 specified columnPartitionKey.
